OL,3,CAfghan data breach a shameful sequel
OL,4,Cto the Kabul horror story
OL,6,FSo the Kabul horror story has a
OL,7,Fshameful sequel. I wonder does the rot
OL,8,Fstop here?
OL,10,FA month from now will see the fourth
OL,11,Fanniversary of the fall of Kabul. The
OL,12,Freturn of the Taliban and the
OL,13,Fwithdrawal of Western troops marked
OL,14,Fone of the most horrendous and
OL,15,Fhumiliating failures in our history.
