OL,6,FWe abandoned Afghanistan more than two
OL,7,Fdecades after participating in the
OL,8,Finitial offensive to topple Osama Bin
OL,9,FLaden's hosts, the tragically
OL,10,Fironically named Operation Enduring
OL,11,FFreedom.
OL,13,FFor a week or so in August 2021,
OL,14,Fsoldiers from the Parachute Regiment
OL,15,Fwere tasked with securing the
OL,16,Fperimeter at Kabul International
OL,17,FAirport so that a massive airlift
OL,18,Fcould take place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
