OL,6,FWatching it first hand, one couldn't
OL,7,Fhelp but marvel as dozens of giant
OL,8,Ftransport planes took off steeply and
OL,9,Fat full power, eager to evade any
OL,10,Fparting shots.
OL,12,FAnd then you reminded yourself of the
OL,13,Fshame that was behind this flight and
OL,14,Fthe consequences for the friends we
OL,15,Fwould inevitably leave behind.
