OL,6,FThe British staging post at the
OL,7,Fairport was called the Baron Hotel.
OL,8,FOne boiling afternoon that August we
OL,9,Fwent to a small side entrance and saw
OL,10,FParas firing warning shots over the
OL,11,Fheads of hundreds of Afghans desperate
OL,12,Fto get into the compound and out of
OL,13,Ftheir country.
OL,15,FSome of these people were waving UK
OL,16,Fpassports, but were denied entry
OL,17,Fnonetheless because their names
OL,18,Fweren't on the approved list.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
