OL,6,FThat was probably the worst week of my
OL,7,Fworking life. It was incredibly
OL,8,Fdepressing, not least because we knew
OL,9,Fwhat was in store for Afghanistan.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe morning after the Taliban re-
OL,17,Fentered Kabul we drove until we were
OL,18,Fstopped at one of their checkpoints.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
